{"tid":245212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[一人一信]Winning Eleven染紅？ 港澳台區旗國旗離奇消失","createTime":"2017-05-16T05:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T07:18:19.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80deb7a2d972644ebe2d233b923db254cd26a39d","tid":245212,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T05:13:33.000Z","msg":"[一人一信]Winning Eleven染紅？ 港澳台區旗國旗離奇消失<br />\n<br />\n日本暢銷足球遊戲《Winning Eleven 2017》，係唔少港男由細玩到大嘅遊戲，可以算得上係香港人嘅集體回憶之一。隻game上年九月中推出嗰陣，仲新增本土元素嘅廣東話旁述，由足球評述員Keyman馬啟仁同前體育主播伍家謙配音。<br />\n<br />\n點知最近隻game疑似染紅，有玩家投訴上個月完成更新後，想創造球員嗰陣，發現香港同澳門區旗、台灣嘅中華民國國旗都離加消失。多年玩家、港大法律系碩士生兼「JR團隊」召集人盧俊宇，對此直言十分詫異。<br />\n<br />\n佢話一直玩開Winning，三支旗都存在，突然冇咗，難免令佢懷疑同政治有關，「你話我會唔會係政治敏感咗 當中係咪會驚得失一啲國家，或者得失中國呀甚至乎，因為咁啱淨係得中國有，澳門、台灣、香港冇，我覺得唔係咁容易解釋到。」<br />\n<br />\n盧坦言好失望，「我想做返個香港人，創造個香港籍嘅球員，嘩，原來我都冇自己既區旗睇到，咁其實仲有咩意思呢。」佢仲話唔少朋友幾乎罷玩。《壹》仔向遊戲製造商Konami查詢，但過咗幾日都未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170514/large/1494754994_4991.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170514%2Flarge%2F1494754994_4991.jpg&h=1348cc7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170514/large/1494754991_ce2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170514%2Flarge%2F1494754991_ce2f.jpg&h=217cb50a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170514/large/1494754997_677f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170514%2Flarge%2F1494754997_677f.jpg&h=7f06088b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170514/large/1494755000_f62a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170514%2Flarge%2F1494755000_f62a.jpg&h=a3178d21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n盧俊宇懷疑港澳台三支旗消失，跟政治有關。"},{"pid":"4ece975096c656ac0bfa7deb1384fb7c6f611fa0","tid":245212,"uid":582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T05:16:22.000Z","msg":"都冇人玩架啦"},{"pid":"9ae7331ab44cf11f5fc77203c6671f00d9743dbd","tid":245212,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T05:19:29.000Z","msg":"加下仲有人玩winning既咩<br />\n個個都好似係Fifa"},{"pid":"6b461949fe2e3312dc467547074dfae336a8b3c5","tid":245212,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T05:25:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加下仲有人玩winning既咩<br />\n個個都好似係Fifa</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02a208f3d576e849a74ece74784e2c8eaf42b21","tid":245212,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T05:46:23.000Z","msg":"咁就咪撚特登配廣東話啦戇鳩"},{"pid":"3f6553ae4e9f7d4fa67d048470c48ed1e6ae5be3","tid":245212,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T05:53:32.000Z","msg":"細個玩 Winning 到而家, 真係貞節牌坊都敗埋"},{"pid":"2cee21a771a7fc151211ad116a61a33a23d1bc87","tid":245212,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T05:59:04.000Z","msg":"依家個個都玩fifa啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b0463a452a0e83b2fb088db83ab1ffd0c33fa4","tid":245212,"uid":76148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:32:18.000Z","msg":"Losing  Eleven"},{"pid":"44ea64159a978b72d9b7e7d6f7c765dd4e5a9c64","tid":245212,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:58:36.000Z","msg":"執柒左佢啦"},{"pid":"6d340ecb6aed4b09b66902a30bb992d3f0dea365","tid":245212,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T07:12:24.000Z","msg":"至少2015已經開始係咁<br />\n2017先有人發現<br />\n真係證明全香港已經改打Fifa"},{"pid":"0354cfc25c147a8abb92ec9dd0a60cc332036329","tid":245212,"uid":34348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T07:18:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>至少2015已經開始係咁<br />\n2017先有人發現<br />\n真係證明全香港已經改打Fifa</blockquote><br />\n因為2017個廣東話先有人買吓（好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}